                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9161" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1378</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1411 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蓬生麻中，不扶而直：D公司内控环境赋能企业创新之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">With the good we become good: D company’s internal control environment empowers the way of enterprise innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李万福，樊雨洁，郑琳青，何卓越，姜文丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">D公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">6 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部控制环境；企业创新；新质生产力；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Internal control environment; Enterprise innovation; New quality productivity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">提高企业创新能力既是加强企业核心竞争力的重要手段，也是加快形成新发展格局的重要举措。以往企业内控环境的主基调是防范风险，但是却忽略了研发部争分夺秒的技术创新需求。本案例描述了在强调防范风险的内控环境下，财务部依据固有流程完成工作，引发预算调整审批流程过长且时间占用过多，以及外地研发项目报销困难的问题，导致研发进度受阻的事件。复现了D公司为助力企业创新而多措并举，授予财务人员更多权力并使其具有服务创新的意识，从而建立能够赋能企业创新的内控环境的过程。本案例旨在引导学员理解及掌握内控环境赋能企业创新之道，并思考在加快实施创新驱动发展战略的背景下，企业应如何完善内控环境以更好地赋能创新，进而加快形成新质生产力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Improving the innovation ability of is not only an important means to strengthen the core competitiveness of enterprises, but also an important measure to accelerate the formation of a new development pattern. In the past, the main tone of the internal control environment of enterprises was to prevent risks, but it ignored the innovation needs. This case describes an incident in which the financial department completed the work according to the inherent process under the internal control environment emphasizing risk prevention, which led to an excessively long and time-consuming approval process for budget adjustment, and difficulties in reimbursement of overseas research and development projects, resulting in the progress of research and development being hindered. This paper reproduces the process of D Company taking multiple measures to help innovation, granting financial personnel more power and making them have the consciousness of service innovation, to establish an internal control environment that can enable enterprise innovation. This case aims to guide students to understand and master the way of internal control environment enabling innovation and consider how enterprises should improve the internal control environment to better enable innovation and accelerate the formation of new quality productivity under the background of accelerating the implementation of innovation-driven development strategy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部控制环境；组织机构设计；企业文化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-01</td>
                            </tr>
